<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
      <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
  </head>
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <body ng-app="starter">
          <div ng-view> 
            <div ng-app='starter' ng-controller='HomeCtrl' class="container">
              <h1>Welcome to the Paine Library</h1>
              <table class="table-striped table-bordered">
                <thead>
                   <tr>
                     <th ng-repeat="header in tblData">{{ header }}</th>
                   </tr>
                </thead>
                <form action="">
                  <tbody>
                    <tr id="row{{rowId}}" ng-repeat="item in books.data" ng-init="rowId = $index">
                      <td><edit-in-place value="item.author"></edit-in-place></td>
                      <td><edit-in-place value="item.title"></edit-in-place></td>
                      <td><edit-in-place value="item.location"></edit-in-place></td>
                      <td><button class="btn btn-primary" ng-click="updateEntry(item.id, item)">Edit</button></td>
                      <td><button class="btn btn-primary" ng-click="deleteEntry(item.id); remove(rowId)">Remove</button></td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </form> 
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% include ../partials/scripts.ejs %>
        </body>
      </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="sidebar">
        
          <form action="http://{{ip}}/books" method="POST" ng-model="ip" value="{{ip}}">
            <p>IP Address: <input type="text" ng-model="ip"> {{ip}}</p>
            <p>Title:
              <input type="text" ng-model="book.title" placeholder="Title of Book" name="title">
            </p>
            <p>Author(s)
              <input type="text" ng-model="book.contributor" placeholder="Author(s)" name="author">
            </p>
            <p>Location: {{location}} 
              <input type="text" ng-model="location" placeholder="Location" name="location" value="N/A">
            </p>
            <input type="submit" value="Submit to Database">

            <p>
        Since feeling is first, who pays attention to the syntax of things will never wholly kiss you, Oh! to be a fool while Spring is in the world, my blood approves, and kisses are better fate than wisdom, Lady I swear by all flowers, Don't cry! The best gesture of my brain is less than your eyelids' flutter, which says, we are for each other. Then laugh, leaning back in my arms, for life is not paragraph, and Death, I think, is no paraenthesis.
          </p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



</html>

